{"tid":188825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳真社取得政府內部參考價 有大廈維修工程只值政府標準四成","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T07:00:34.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db9a6d13d08e3d5845a23e6ac8eac3e94cfb0189","tid":188825,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳真社取得政府內部參考價 有大廈維修工程只值政府標準四成</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/cdfbba_4b811e0adf594482830c418baaae416b~mv2_d_4454_2969_s_4_2.jpg/v1/fill/w_1212,h_808,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/cdfbba_4b811e0adf594482830c418baaae416b~mv2_d_4454_2969_s_4_2.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fcdfbba_4b811e0adf594482830c418baaae416b~mv2_d_4454_2969_s_4_2.jpg%2Fv1%2Ffill%2Fw_1212%2Ch_808%2Cal_c%2Cq_85%2Cusm_0.66_1.00_0.01%2Fcdfbba_4b811e0adf594482830c418baaae416b~mv2_d_4454_2969_s_4_2.webp&h=f556a81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(傳真社香港6日電) - 本港樓宇維修圍標問題嚴重，各界都希望有合理維修價作參考，協助業主篩選標書，惟政府一直未能提供。但FactWire傳真社發現，政府物業工程招標時，會參考一份整合過去工程費製成的維修項目價格清單，以防工程被圍標。傳真社取得有關文件，並聘請獨立專業人士利用數據為3個住宅維修項目估價，結果其中兩個工程費只值政府標準的四成，包括捲入2.63億元圍標案的沙田翠湖花園，以及一個仍在進行的樓宇維修項目；換言之，相關業主在市場資訊不足之下，多付超過1.5倍維修費。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社取得房屋署物業維修項目價格清單，是政府為公共物業進行工程招標時，評估承建商入標價的參考文件。一名曾在房屋署參與撰寫物業維修項目價格清單的消息人士，確認有關文件真偽，並指業界普遍稱之為「天書」。「天書」由房屋署轄下屋邨管理處的工料測量組出版，約有1,000頁，分為兩部分，內容涵蓋搭棚、石屎、喉管、外牆砌磚、油漆等28類工程，包括超過15,000個連工包料的項目單價，以及各項施工、監工標準等，本社取得2013年及2014年兩個版本。<br />\n<br />\n詳盡報道已發佈至新聞媒體用戶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/04/06/傳真社取得政府內部參考價-有大廈維修工程只值政府標準四成\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsingle-post%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2F%E5%82%B3%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E5%83%B9-%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%AA%E5%80%BC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=9fc51721\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/04/06/傳真社取得政府內部參考價-有大廈維修工程只值政府標準四成</a>"},{"pid":"a05b127fc24fd38588646a1d42041a9dfffebc67","tid":188825,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"997cd13697ec8cf7a4ed23ec0bdf53eb380d2633","tid":188825,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"80c7a85a7cb05b67990b8c81ae9c6972532a6295","tid":188825,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"本野有無公開出黎？"},{"pid":"ec16cd0d23a77b3a240ae81da0d0143e686b004b","tid":188825,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本野有無公開出黎？</blockquote><br />\n會俾人告（好似係）"},{"pid":"690b419581505e2c31a63510f52846c0cd4a8689","tid":188825,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本野有無公開出黎？</blockquote><br />\n會俾人告（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n拎去外國用starbuck wifi upload應該捉唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"95963f718c182af5b5a4275f1df5ebd531a667bd","tid":188825,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"點解傳真社可以咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0a662c36784add14d7945ae99cc81004a9ccc8","tid":188825,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本野有無公開出黎？</blockquote><br />\n會俾人告（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n呢本野好似唔會公開，但係好多公司都會有一分流出版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f86058e3815119cba9f44cb0c55625488116d78","tid":188825,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本野有無公開出黎？</b